name: Jane Doe and the Astronaut
description:
The Little Astronaut thinks shes on an adventure on another planet. Jane Doe knows that they are both dead. Together they search for Jane Doe's missing body parts as Jane Doe protects The Little Astronaut from the truth.

Small project for :https://itch.io/jam/my-first-game-jam-summer-2020

Hope to come back to finish and polish it. Currently in a rough state. I would call it a complete game though! Hope you like my very first game, Jane Doe and the Astronaut.
